[src:elliptic-functions/lemniscate-elliptic-functions-p02] The lemniscate functions are closely related to the Weierstrass elliptic function $\wp (z;1,0)$ (the "lemniscatic case"), with invariants ⁠ $g_{2}=1$ ⁠ and ⁠ $g_{3}=0$ ⁠.
