[src:elliptic-functions/lemniscate-elliptic-functions-p02] Some authors instead define the Hurwitz numbers as $\mathrm {H} _{n}'=\mathrm {H} _{4n}$ .
[src:elliptic-functions/lemniscate-elliptic-functions-p02] A **quartic residue** (mod p ) is any number congruent to the fourth power of an integer.
